  "text": "The rest of the paper is organized as follows. Section 2 describes the scenarios where our method is useful. Section 3 overviews related work. Section 4 discusses the method in [CITATION_1] whose allocation we aim to reproduce without the knowledge of the SPM size. Section 5 discusses our method in detail from the profiling stage to embedded loading stage. Section 6 discusses the allocation policy used in the embedded loader. Section 7 describes how program codes are allocated into SPM. Section 8 presents the experimental environment, benchmarks properties, and our method's results. Section 9 concludes.",
